583
00:26:27,310 --> 00:26:28,880
and Mr. Zhang also told me.

584
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,510
So I'm checking with you again

585
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:33,270
and invite you to share

586
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:35,030
Xiao Youguang's deeds with us,

587
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:36,110
okay?

588
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:37,880
Forget it.

589
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:39,000
In such settings,

590
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,480
let the leaders speak.

591
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:43,590
You're his family,
so you'd be more suitable,

592
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,630
right?

593
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:47,020
Just make sure you're on time.

594
00:26:47,030 --> 00:26:48,270
I'll meet you at the door.

595
00:26:49,310 --> 00:26:50,920
Alright, I won't keep you.

596
00:26:50,920 --> 00:26:51,760
See you there.

597
00:26:51,770 --> 00:26:52,620
- Okay.
- Thank you.

598
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:53,870
You're too kind.

599
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:55,430
Mom,

600
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:56,590
don't go.

601
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,830
They've forgotten

602
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,310
about Xiao Youguang's deeds,

603
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,840
so why should you remind them?

604
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:05,790
Why bring up our pain

605
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,720
and make them remember?

606
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,750
Then they'll gossip

607
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:08,920
about it.

608
00:27:10,350 --> 00:27:11,310
What's the point?

609
00:27:22,820 --> 00:27:25,180
(Shanghai Puyang No. 2 Middle School)

