611
00:27:27,140 --> 00:27:28,260
(Preface)

612
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:30,430
What's this?

613
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:32,350
The Olympiad Math materials.

614
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,510
I made a copy for you.

615
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,790
You didn't make the Team this time.

616
00:27:37,120 --> 00:27:37,970
But don't worry.

617
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:39,350
There's another chance.

618
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:40,880
I'll be waiting for you.

619
00:27:41,890 --> 00:27:42,800
Actually,

620
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:45,450
not everyone has Chang Wuji's talent.

621
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:47,680
So it's normal to use some extra help.

622
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,750
Thank you for your concern,

623
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:50,310
