624
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:54,110
Xiao Han,

625
00:27:56,870 --> 00:27:58,110
you eventually figured out about

626
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:59,750
about the Self-Reliance Scholarship.

627
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:01,310
Be realistic.

628
00:28:01,990 --> 00:28:04,340
A second prize in the competition
grants college admission.

629
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:06,960
Even a third prize gets you extra points.

630
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,110
Is being so aloof really worth it?

631
00:28:21,790 --> 00:28:23,480
Zhao Tingting is the only girl in our grade

632
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:24,550
who made the Team.

633
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:25,670
She's amazing.

634
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,640
Chang Wuji is more impressive.

635
00:28:27,690 --> 00:28:29,390
Finished in 30 minutes and topped the class.

636
00:28:30,590 --> 00:28:32,270
Xiao Han didn't make it.

637
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:34,310
He fell from grace.

638
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,510
Brother Xiao Han.

639
00:28:56,840 --> 00:28:58,110
You eventually figured out about

640
00:28:58,110 --> 00:28:59,790
about the Self-Reliance Scholarship.

641
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:01,240
Be realistic.

642
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,920
Is being so aloof really worth it?

643
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,440
You're the butler's son.

644
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:05,280
Even if we can't be heros,

645
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,750
but we can't be cowards either.

646
00:29:06,750 --> 00:29:08,110
We should tell the kids sooner.

647
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:11,000
That way, I can take care of you both.

648
00:29:11,010 --> 00:29:11,920
You're selfish.

649
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:13,310
I can't stand people like you.

650
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:28,110
What's it gonna be?

651
00:29:29,110 --> 00:29:30,350
First it's tomorrow,

652
00:29:30,510 --> 00:29:31,440
then it's the day after?

653
00:29:38,510 --> 00:29:39,680
If you don't have it tomorrow,

654
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:41,510
I'll report this to your school.

655
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,750
I know your class

656
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:45,160
and your name.

657
00:29:47,640 --> 00:29:48,480
Did you hear me?

658
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:51,790
What are you staring at?

659
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:53,320
Get lost.

660
00:29:57,770 --> 00:29:58,710
Darn it.

661
00:29:59,310 --> 00:30:00,150
Look at him.

662
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,960
Last time you knew not to interfere.

663
00:30:03,590 --> 00:30:04,510
Get lost now.

664
00:30:09,590 --> 00:30:11,350
I said, get lost!

665
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,040
Get lost!

666
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:28,630
Xiao Han!

667
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,960
You're going too far.

668
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:45,940
- Chen Mo, ride faster.
- Xiao Han!

669
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,550
And Liu Jianfeng.

670
00:30:53,510 --> 00:30:54,350
Chen Mo!

671
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,000
Chen Mo!

672
00:30:57,790 --> 00:30:58,830
You're tough, huh?

673
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:00,720
Ka Men, go get the teacher.

674
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:01,870
Be careful.

675
00:31:03,720 --> 00:31:04,560
Stop it!

676
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:14,840
- Chen Mo!
- The lovely lady from before.

677
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,000
What?

678
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:19,560
Chen Mo.

679
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:26,000
- Come on.
- Put it down.

680
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,310
You wanna die, huh?

681
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:30,280
Put it down.

682
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:34,430
Get people.

683
00:31:35,240 --> 00:31:36,440
- Mao Tou!
- Brother Xiao Han.

684
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,240
Chen Mo!

685
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:53,520
Mao Tou!

686
00:31:55,370 --> 00:31:56,430
Get away!

687
00:31:57,830 --> 00:31:58,700
Get away!

688
00:32:02,110 --> 00:32:02,960
Are you okay?

689
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:15,560
Xiao Han!

690
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:38,480
You guys really have some nerve.

691
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,400
Fighting in groups.

692
00:32:44,110 --> 00:32:45,990
Is this what you should do?

693
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,040
Ms. Wu,

694
00:32:48,750 --> 00:32:49,640
actually,

695
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:51,280
this isn't…

696
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,880
This isn't their fault.

697
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:54,310
They were just saving me.

698
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:55,720
It was those thugs...

699
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,640
Did I ask you to speak?

700
00:32:57,350 --> 00:32:58,350
No matter the reason,

701
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,400
no matter the cause,

702
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:01,160
fighting is never right.

703
00:33:07,590 --> 00:33:09,480
Integrity, diligence, responsibility,

704
00:33:11,750 --> 00:33:12,590
virtue…

705
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:14,540
Stop looking!

706
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,590
Remember them well.

707
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,280
From now on,

708
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:24,550
this must never happen again.

709
00:33:24,730 --> 00:33:25,590
Got it?

710
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,440
Got it.

711
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:27,960
Got it?

712
00:33:28,350 --> 00:33:29,190
Got it.

713
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:35,440
Each of you

714
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:36,750
write a self-reflection.

715
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:39,640
I will personally read them.

716
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:41,680
Hand them in tomorrow.

717
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:42,950
Dismissed.

718
00:33:45,570 --> 00:33:46,750
Ms. Wu, this way.

719
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,310
Oh, this is your school.

720
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,350
Are you two okay?

721
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:56,510
- I'm fine.
- Let's go, boss.

722
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:57,790
- And you?
- I'm fine.

723
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:58,790
Are you alright?

724
00:33:59,790 --> 00:34:01,400
- You go first.
- You're all dirty.

725
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:02,240
I'll head off then.

726
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,320
Are you…

727
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:08,030
Are you all okay?

728
00:34:08,540 --> 00:34:10,320
- I'll go get a first-aid kit.
- We're fine.

729
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,110
What on earth happened today?

730
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,400
There were like 30 girls watching me

731
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,240
play basketball.

732
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,400
Why did you start fighting?

733
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,480
- Yeah.
- Who started it?

734
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:20,800
Xiao Han.

735
00:34:23,440 --> 00:34:24,480
Really?

736
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:28,440
You should've seen it.

737
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:30,000
Xiao Han was so fierce today.

738
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:31,480
Facing the thug leader,

739
00:34:31,480 --> 00:34:32,670
Xiao Han grabbed

740
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:33,510
his neck.

741
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:44,150
They were several of them,

742
00:34:44,510 --> 00:34:46,760
so I thought I'd just accept it.

743
00:34:47,230 --> 00:34:48,400
I didn't expect Xiao Han

744
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,400
to fight three thugs for me.

745
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:51,800
When I saw that,

746
00:34:52,170 --> 00:34:53,850
I got so fired up

747
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:54,880
and…

748
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:56,480
and I also jumped in.

749
00:34:58,670 --> 00:34:59,880
It wasn't just for you.

750
00:35:00,230 --> 00:35:01,440
I did it for myself too.

751
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,400
I was pissed off

752
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,800
and

753
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:06,480
need to vent.

754
00:35:08,630 --> 00:35:09,670
Brother Xiao Han,

755
00:35:10,480 --> 00:35:11,840
with your face like this,

756
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:14,000
how will you explain it?

757
00:35:14,800 --> 00:35:15,960
I will tell the truth.

758
00:35:16,940 --> 00:35:17,800
With bruises like this,

759
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,190
if I say I fell,

760
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:20,400
she wouldn't buy it.

761
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,280
So…

762
00:35:22,670 --> 00:35:23,960
just say it like that?

763
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,960
Yeah. Fighting

764
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:27,550
and failing to make the Team,

765
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,510
which will shatter her image

766
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:31,150
of me,

767
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,360
her perfect son.

768
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,960
That's not too bad.

769
00:35:35,140 --> 00:35:37,490
At least you don't have to be
the perfect kid all the time.

770
00:35:38,590 --> 00:35:39,430
Come on.

771
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:41,360
- Quick, put it here.
- Thanks.

772
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:43,720
Grab some alcohol for disinfecting.

773
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:48,190
But speaking of it,

774
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:49,200
Jianfeng,

775
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:52,440
is it because you dress too flashy?

776
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,920
You look wealthy.

777
00:35:54,590 --> 00:35:55,710
They've been on to you.

778
00:35:55,870 --> 00:35:56,720
Got it?

779
00:35:56,800 --> 00:35:58,150
Actually, my whole outfit,

780
00:35:58,150 --> 00:36:00,030
clothes, pants, shoes, everything,

781
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:01,880
aren't bought from malls.

782
00:36:04,960 --> 00:36:05,800
Qian Jiayue,

783
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:09,510
thanks for keeping my secret.

784
00:36:13,260 --> 00:36:15,190
(Self-Reliance Scholarship Application Form)
There's a scholarship.

785
00:36:15,190 --> 00:36:16,850
(No poor student should be left behind)
You should apply for it.

786
00:36:17,550 --> 00:36:18,800
I don't need it.

787
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:22,590
Mr. Zhou said your family…

788
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:23,430
Thanks, though.

789
00:36:23,990 --> 00:36:25,030
I'm off to play basketball.

790
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:30,150
My dad is on long-term sick leave.

791
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,670
My mom is laid off.

792
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,480
She sells tea eggs outside a company.

793
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:38,590
They've sent me to sports school
since I was little.

794
00:36:38,590 --> 00:36:39,430
Maybe they hoped

795
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:42,230
I'd have a future path.

796
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:45,000
But I disappointed them.

797
00:36:46,030 --> 00:36:47,710
High jump didn't work.

798
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,630
Sprints

799
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:50,840
didn't either.

800
00:36:51,190 --> 00:36:52,800
In the end,

801
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:54,150
I switched to hurdles.

802
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:55,800
My classmates at my old school

803
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,070
all looked down on me.

804
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:01,360
I was afraid you would too.

805
00:37:02,670 --> 00:37:03,760
So I bought these

806
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:05,030
from them.

807
00:37:06,070 --> 00:37:07,030
So

808
00:37:07,030 --> 00:37:08,230
you knew them before?

809
00:37:08,870 --> 00:37:10,150
No, I didn't.

810
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:11,820
One day after school, I saw them

811
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:12,880
selling brand-name goods

812
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:13,840
at the school gate,

813
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:15,820
and claimed
they would sell them for 200,

814
00:37:15,960 --> 00:37:17,610
but the original price were over 1,000

815
00:37:17,830 --> 00:37:19,630
because they are stolen from a factory.

816
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,550
I couldn't resist.

817
00:37:24,590 --> 00:37:25,430
I bought them

818
00:37:25,670 --> 00:37:27,360
with money from my grandma.

819
00:37:27,590 --> 00:37:29,550
I didn't dare tell my parents.

820
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:33,150
These aren't stolen at all.

821
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:36,190
They're fakes from Qipu Road.

822
00:37:36,190 --> 00:37:37,190
200?

823
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,670
I wouldn't pay 50 for them.

824
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,070
And then what happened?

825
00:37:42,550 --> 00:37:44,030
Then they blackmailed me,

826
00:37:44,670 --> 00:37:46,670
saying I had to pay 1,200

827
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:47,840
for these clothes.

828
00:37:48,590 --> 00:37:50,070
If I don't,

829
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,320
they'd report me to the school,

830
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:53,920
claiming I joined them,

831
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:55,480
in stealing from factories.

832
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:57,310
That's extortion.

833
00:37:57,710 --> 00:37:58,630
So horrible.

834
00:37:58,630 --> 00:37:59,470
Exactly.

835
00:37:59,670 --> 00:38:01,360
Over a thousand.

836
00:38:02,030 --> 00:38:03,670
Where did you get the money?

837
00:38:05,010 --> 00:38:06,150
So…

838
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:08,070
So I…

839
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:12,880
So you acted on impulse...

840
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,630
Case solved!

841
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:17,240
You took the lunch money.

842
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:20,360
I regretted it soon after.

843
00:38:20,670 --> 00:38:21,510
I'm sorry.

844
00:38:21,630 --> 00:38:22,800
I'm so sorry.

845
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:23,800
Really sorry, everyone.

846
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,440
I already told them.

847
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,340
If they bother me again,

848
00:38:27,530 --> 00:38:29,070
I have nothing to give but my life.

849
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:30,230
Kill me if they dare.

850
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:31,110
Next time, call the police.

851
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:31,950
That's right.

852
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:34,880
We'll stick together.

853
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:36,550
Together to school, together home.

854
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,030
If they come again,

855
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:39,000
we won't be afraid.

856
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:41,480
Yes, your issues are ours.

857
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:42,760
We'll always stick together.

858
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,960
Let's see who dares bully you.

859
00:38:58,670 --> 00:38:59,510
Thanks.

860
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,550
No need to thank us. Let's go.

861
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:02,710
Let's walk him home together.

862
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:03,550
- Okay.
- Let's go.

863
00:39:06,230 --> 00:39:07,670
I have to return the first aid kit.

864
00:39:08,040 --> 00:39:09,540
Hurry, or no time for self-reflection.

865
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:13,190
You two, hurry up.

866
00:39:13,190 --> 00:39:14,320
Wait for me at the bike shed.

867
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:15,800
See you in a bit.

